<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <title>ERROR 404 - 해당 URL은 존재하지 않습니다.</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
